# Design slot

This folder holds the paired `.pen` baseline for this base. The Pencil
file accumulates section-component designs that map 1:1 with the
components in `src/components/sections/`.

The .pen file is added in a follow-up commit when the design pass runs
in the Pencil app. See `bytetalent/docs/guide-pencil.md` for the
Pencil MCP workflow.
